trans-unit.source: Occurs when the file listing pattern, such as "*.\*", is changed by setting the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.FileName*> or <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Pattern*> property in code.

trans-unit.source: You can use a `PatternChange` event procedure to respond to pattern changes in a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke en `PatternChange` hendelsesprosedyren å svare på mønsteret endringer i en <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontroll.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: When you assign a string that contains a new pattern to the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.FileName%2A> property, the FileListBox invokes the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.PathChange> event.
trans-unit.target: Når du tilordner en streng som inneholder et nytt mønster til den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.FileName%2A>egenskapen FileListBox aktiverer den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.PathChange>hendelsen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.PathChange> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.FileName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"></xref> control contains files that have read-only attributes.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som bestemmer om en <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"> </xref> kontrollen inneholder filer som har attributtet skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: Use the `ReadOnly` property for a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control to specify whether files that have read-only attributes are displayed in the file list or not.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av `ReadOnly` -egenskapen for et <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontroll for å angi om filer som har skrivebeskyttelsen skal vises i listen eller ikke.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A> property is set to `true` (the default), files that have read-only attributes are displayed regardless of the `ReadOnly` property setting.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A>er satt til `true` (standard), vises filer som har skrivebeskyttelsen uavhengig av den `ReadOnly` egenskapsinnstillingen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox.Normal%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if files that have the <xref uid="langword_csharp_ReadOnly" name="ReadOnly" href=""></xref> attribute will be displayed; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis filer som har den <xref uid="langword_csharp_ReadOnly" name="ReadOnly" href=""> </xref> attributtet blir vist; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Forces the control to invalidate its client area and immediately redraw itself.
trans-unit.target: Tvinger kontrollen for å gjøre det klientområdet og tegne umiddelbart seg selv.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the items in a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"></xref> are sorted alphabetically.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om elementene i en <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"> </xref> sorteres alfabetisk.

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control, `Sorted` always returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontroll, `Sorted` returnerer alltid `false`.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if items in the control are sorted; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementene i kontrollen sorteres; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that determines whether a <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"></xref> control displays files that have <xref uid="langword_csharp_System" name="System" href=""></xref> attributes.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som bestemmer om en <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox"> </xref> kontrollen viser filer som har <xref uid="langword_csharp_System" name="System" href=""> </xref> attributter.

trans-unit.source: Use this property to specify the type of files to display in a <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control, based on standard `System` file attribute used in the operating environment.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne egenskapen til å angi hvilken type filer skal vises i en <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontroll, basert på standard `System` file-attributtet som brukes i drift miljøet.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: Setting this property at run time resets the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox> control to display only those files that have the specified attribute.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du setter denne egenskapen på kjøretidspunktet tilbakestiller den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>kontrollen skal vises bare filer med det angitte attributtet.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.FileListBox>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if files that have the <xref uid="langword_csharp_System" name="System" href=""></xref> attribute will be displayed; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis filer som har den <xref uid="langword_csharp_System" name="System" href=""> </xref> attributtet blir vist; ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.
